Articles.Content:
I had not dig into the actual name change. However, the following is confirmed through a quick glance that we have actual "new" parts:

// Mk1 Command Pod
mk1pod.v2

// HECS
probeCoreHex.v2

// OKTO
probeCoreOcto.v2

// OKTO2
probeCoreOcto2.v2

// RoveMate
roverBody.v2

// Stayputnik
probeCoreSphere.v2

// RT-5 "Flea" Solid Fuel Booster
solidBooster.sm.v2

// RT-10 "Hammer" Solid Fuel Booster
solidBooster.v2

The following is unable to find the duplicate, and thus assume to be drop in replacement (no convertion needed)
* HECS2
* QBE
* FL-T100 
* FL-T200
* FL-T400
* FL-T800

I will dig up the text file name when I am less busy tommorrow.

Edited October 17, 2018 by Jestersage
